 &lt;p&gt;üåóüåëüåëüåëüåë&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvZXh0ZXJuYWwvMTAwL3AxMDA1NS5wZGY=&#34;&gt;È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhw&#34;&gt;Online Judge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudWRlYnVnLmNvbS9VVmEvMTAwNTU=&#34;&gt;uDebug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time limit: 3.000 seconds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆ&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆ&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆ&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hashmat is a brave warrior who with his group of young soldiers moves from one place to another to fight against his opponents. Before Fighting he just calculates one thing, the difference between his soldier number and the opponent‚Äôs soldier number. From this difference he decides whether to fight or not. Hashmat‚Äôs soldier number is never greater than his opponent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The input contains two numbers in every line. These two numbers in each line denotes the number soldiers in Hashmat‚Äôs army and his opponent‚Äôs army or vice versa. The input numbers are not greater than 232. Input is terminated by ‚ÄòEnd of File‚Äô.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For each line of input, print the difference of number of soldiers between Hashmat‚Äôs army and his opponent‚Äôs army. Each output should be in seperate line.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;10 12&lt;br /&gt;
10 14&lt;br /&gt;
100 200&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2&lt;br /&gt;
4&lt;br /&gt;
100&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
