 &lt;p&gt;üåïüåëüåëüåëüåë&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvZXh0ZXJuYWwvMTAwL3AxMDAzOC5wZGY=&#34;&gt;È°åÁõÆÈÄ£Áµê&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhw&#34;&gt;Online Judge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudWRlYnVnLmNvbS9VVmEvMTAwMzg=&#34;&gt;uDebug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆË™™Êòé&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time limit: 3.000 seconds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;È°åÁõÆ&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#È°åÁõÆ&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; È°åÁõÆ&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A sequence of n &amp;gt; 0 integers is called a jolly jumper if the absolute values of the difference between successive elements take on all the values 1 through n ‚àí 1. For instance,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 4 2 3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;is a jolly jumper, because the absolutes differences are 3, 2, and 1 respectively. The definition implies that any sequence of a single integer is a jolly jumper. You are to write a program to determine whether or not each of a number of sequences is a jolly jumper.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each line of input contains an integer n ‚â§ 3000 followed by n integers representing the sequence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For each line of input, generate a line of output saying ‚ÄòJolly‚Äô or ‚ÄòNot jolly‚Äô.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4 1 4 2 3&lt;br /&gt;
5 1 4 2 -1 6&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jolly&lt;br /&gt;
Not jolly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Ëß£È°åÊäÄÂ∑ß&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
